{"tid":2261593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一位自稱喬的競選人員發文：我為幫拜登助選感到羞恥","createTime":"2020-10-28T12:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T16:56:23.000Z","uid":175208,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"931109bf541f99e8124a053bce5013b42a55893a","tid":2261593,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/122897976_3544709795623189_4306049274229921591_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=sV03vqkIUZcAX-7nSZc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=39a6b30df144bbc8b1236690252468f8&amp;oe=5FBD6387\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F122897976_3544709795623189_4306049274229921591_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DsV03vqkIUZcAX-7nSZc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D39a6b30df144bbc8b1236690252468f8%26oe%3D5FBD6387&h=cd5dbbcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國時間25日，一個自稱曾是喬前競選幹部的帳號於美國論壇4chan發文，稱後悔幫拜登競選且為曾支持拜登感到羞恥😨<br />\n<br />\n在文章上，他另外附上一張競選辦公室的照片，而內容也陳述他們在撥打拜票電話時幾乎遭受到不小的打擊，這都是因為拜登的腐敗所引起😲<br />\n<br />\n內文翻譯：<br />\n喬競選活動內幕<br />\n<br />\n雖然沒有人在談論，但是每個人臉上的表情都說明了一切，這場競選已經完了！ 我為幫喬從事競選活動而感到羞恥，然而，我並不是唯一這樣的人。 最近幾天，有幾名競選人員和志願者都退出了會議。 基本上這裡就像是荒廢的鬼城。 發佈此貼文後，我也將離開，並且再也不會回到這裡。<br />\n<br />\n喬貪腐，而他的家人有嚴重的問題。 喬不可能贏得這次選舉了。 我們打了那麼多電話，敲了很多門。 基本上不少人告訴我們馬上滾開，但更大多數人會聽個幾秒鐘，然後告訴我們他們不感興趣，但從他們說話的方式，你就是知道他們永遠不會考慮投票給喬。<br />\n<br />\n所有事情真的很詭異。我已經參與競選活動超過十年了，今年人們對我們的回應方式有很大不同。 無論如何，我認為你們可能想聽到最真實的話。 在我遠離這場競選活動之前，至少，面對所有的謊言之中，我能幫忙揭露一些真相。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/milkteawo/photos/a.3414405455320291/3544709792289856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmilkteawo%2Fphotos%2Fa.3414405455320291%2F3544709792289856%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7CVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=9a126970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/milkteawo/photos/a.3414405455320291/3544709792289856/</a>"},{"pid":"7ef004b781fe8fb6903a9461f98e196e0cb14263","tid":2261593,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:25:41.000Z","msg":"真相呢"},{"pid":"755a77eede71df316f542f6f689a2ddf0e57108a","tid":2261593,"uid":295230,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:26:09.000Z","msg":"4chan<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82087e773c25d6ceae2baf97f8f30cd9e8f555d9","tid":2261593,"uid":236368,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"假嘅，我唔會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592af054328665de0395257b8f4513f15403e529","tid":2261593,"uid":103922,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:28:00.000Z","msg":"4chan<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e515f11289b8612bcde501cb781d8f916b86192b","tid":2261593,"uid":76310,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"睇下民調啦<br />\n登登仲贏8%"},{"pid":"bb0267aa66b016d89c0ade7c858bf673d1ddeed4","tid":2261593,"uid":175208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e515f11289b8612bcde501cb781d8f916b86192b","tid":2261593,"uid":76310,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"睇下民調啦<br />\n登登仲贏8%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a54337ad1c828681ee8d8813de4a81be12f3e5c","tid":2261593,"uid":57862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"joke 2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7fa20df4505fc2b575c577f89212f7fb494988","tid":2261593,"uid